OL,3,CChief Constable apologises again to
OL,4,CKatie Simpson's family
OL,6,FThe chief constable has warned anyone
OL,7,Fwho uses inappropriate behaviour
OL,8,Fwithin the PSNI will "very quickly
OL,9,Flose your job".
OL,11,FJon Boutcher updated the Policing
OL,12,FBoard following the publication of an
OL,13,Findependent review into the death of
OL,14,Fshowjumper Katie Simpson in 2020.
OL,16,FHe revealed that the force receives
OL,17,Fnearly 16 reports of violence against
OL,18,Fwomen and girls every day.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@NO]
