OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778253065
OL,3,CChief Constable apologises again to
OL,4,CKatie Simpson's family
OL,6,FMs Simpson, 21, from Tynan, Co Armagh,
OL,7,Fdied in Altnagelvin Area Hospital
OL,8,Falmost a week after an incident in
OL,9,FGortnessy Meadows, Lettershandoney.
OL,11,FPolice originally thought she had
OL,12,Ftaken her own life.
OL,14,FIt was not until the following year
OL,15,Fthat Jonathan Creswell, the partner of
OL,16,FMs Simpson's sister, was arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
