OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778253065
OL,3,CChief Constable apologises again to
OL,4,CKatie Simpson's family
OL,6,FHe said: "There were a number of
OL,7,Fabsolutely unacceptable police
OL,8,Ffailings, many have been previously
OL,9,Fidentified, including the failure to
OL,10,Frefer Creswell to the public
OL,11,Fprotection arrangements in Northern
OL,12,FIreland or have his previous serious
OL,13,Foffending, easily searched on the
OL,14,Fpolice system."
OL,16,FThe Chief Constable said officers
OL,17,F"lacked professional curiosity" and
OL,18,F"too readily accepted Creswell's lies".
OL,26,@nD@JOUvD@OO]yD@AOUyD@_O]zD@AOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778253065
OL,3,CChief Constable apologises again to
OL,4,CKatie Simpson's family
OL,6,FHe said: "These failings and not
OL,7,Finvestigating concerns raised by a
OL,8,Fnumber of people allowed Creswell to
OL,9,Favoid being treated as a suspect for
OL,10,Fsome five months, causing further
OL,11,Funnecessary pain and trauma to Katie's
OL,12,Ffamily."
OL,14,FMr Boutcher added: "Let me be clear,
OL,15,Fwhen Katie was admitted to hospital in
OL,16,FAugust of 2020, we absolutely failed
OL,17,Fher.
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@HO]vD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
