PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778253065
OL,3,CChief Constable apologises again to
OL,4,CKatie Simpson's family
OL,6,F"We did not treat her death as
OL,7,Fsuspicious until January of 2021, when
OL,8,Fthe investigation very quickly found
OL,9,Fcompelling evidence to charge Creswell
OL,10,Fwith her murder.
OL,12,F"I previously personally apologised to
OL,13,Fthe family for these failings, and I
OL,14,Fdo so again now."
OL,16,FThe Chief Constable said he had spoken
OL,17,Fto the entire organisation about
OL,18,Fstandards and behaviours.
OL,20,FHe added: "No one, no one should
OL,21,Faccept inappropriate behaviour.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@QO]|D@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778253065
OL,3,CChief Constable apologises again to
OL,4,CKatie Simpson's family
OL,6,F"The PSNI will deal with such
OL,7,Fbehaviour in the strongest possible
OL,8,Fterms,
OL,10,F"I will seek criminal sanctions
OL,11,Fagainst such behaviour, and we have a
OL,12,Fzero tolerance for it.
OL,14,F"At the very least, you will quickly
OL,15,Flose your job.
OL,17,F"We must remember the overwhelming
OL,18,Fmajority of our workforce are
OL,19,Fprofessional with the highest of
OL,20,Fstandards and work tirelessly to keep
OL,21,Fpeople safe.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
