OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1778253065
OL,3,CChief Constable apologises again to
OL,4,CKatie Simpson's family
OL,6,F"They will be devastated by this
OL,7,Freport."
OL,9,FMr Boutcher said violence against
OL,10,Fwomen and girls is a "major threat to
OL,11,Four wider society".
OL,13,FHe said: "Most recent figures show
OL,14,Fthat 22,000 offences were recorded
OL,15,Fover a 12-month period, that is nearly
OL,16,F16 crimes a day."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@HO]rD@VOUsD@RO]uD@JOUxD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
