OL,3,CChief Constable apologises again to
OL,4,CKatie Simpson's family
OL,6,FMr Boutcher added: "As an
OL,7,Forganisation, we are now very much
OL,8,Fvictim-focused, and we are tackling
OL,9,Fviolence against women and girls as an
OL,10,Fabsolute priority within the
OL,11,Forganisation."
